# This directory is populated at runtime by track agents.
# Per-track subdirectories (A/, B/, ... G/) contain:
#   - progress.ndjson   (append-only status log)
#   - artifacts.json    (final artifact metadata on success)
#   - done.flag         (success signal, mutually exclusive with blocker.md)
#   - blocker.md        (failure details, no done.flag written)
#
# See v0/SHARED.md for the full contract.
